0xDD75460A.name: CREATE_VEHICLE

params.name: modelHash
params.description: The model of vehicle to spawn.

params.name: heading
params.description: Heading to face towards, in degrees.

params.name: isNetwork
params.description: Whether to create a network object for the vehicle. If false, the vehicle exists only locally.

params.name: netMissionEntity
params.description: Whether to register the vehicle as pinned to the script host in the R\* network model.

0xDD75460A.description:
Creates a vehicle with the specified model at the specified position. This vehicle will initially be owned by the creating
script as a mission entity, and the model should be loaded already (e.g. using REQUEST_MODEL).

```
NativeDB Added Parameter 8: BOOL p7
```

**This is the server-side RPC native equivalent of the client native [CREATE_VEHICLE](?\_0xAF35D0D2583051B0).**
0xDD75460A.resultsDescription: A script handle (fwScriptGuid index) for the vehicle, or `0` if the vehicle failed to be created.
